{"tid":1534711,"cid":6,"subCid":0,"title":"沙夏：文尼比沙拿更穩 金球排名對他不公","createTime":"2019-09-03T05:49:54.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-03T13:42:13.000Z","uid":19552,"like":35,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":35,"replies":[{"pid":"6f1bb6c17f61d1f9c2ebe159dd9028c45b24b715","tid":1534711,"uid":19552,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-03T05:49:54.000Z","msg":"近日，利物浦天王雲迪積克（Virgil van Dijk）表態稱法明奴（B.Firmino）是自己共事過的最佳球員。這一言論遭到曼聯名宿沙夏（L.Saha）的反對，沙夏認為，文尼（S.Mane）才是利物浦最好的球員。<br />\n<br />\n  沙夏稱：「對我來說，文尼才是利物浦最穩定的球員。他在每一場比賽里都是威脅性十足的。」<br />\n<br />\n  「我們有時會看到沙拿狀態不佳、缺乏靈感，但文尼卻一直非常穩定。」<br />\n<br />\n  「文尼在金球獎的評選中被低估了。我知道為何雲迪積克選擇法明奴當最佳隊友，因為當雲迪積克面對壓力時，他能把球傳給法明奴，法明奴能幫助雲迪積克獲得喘息的機會。」<br />\n<br />\n  「文尼真的被低估了。舉例來說，金球獎的評選就驚到我了，文尼竟然沒進入前十名！對我來說，這個結果太震驚了。他是利物浦最穩定的球員，比沙拿更穩定。當沙拿7、8場比賽不入球的時候，文尼一直能帶領著球隊。」<br />\n<br />\n  「這或許就是文尼被換下時十分不滿的原因。」<br />\n<img src=\"https://f.sinaimg.cn/sports/transform/595/w399h196/20190901/81d5-icxmqsw3732206.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Ff.sinaimg.cn%2Fsports%2Ftransform%2F595%2Fw399h196%2F20190901%2F81d5-icxmqsw3732206.gif&h=ea942478&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"d78ad987a95a32eb3a9fc3fb1e6b330bfe21e55d","tid":1534711,"uid":123991,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-03T05:50:05.000Z","msg":"<div style=\"text-align: center;\"><strong>9月7日 (六) 1PM<br />\n機場交通壓力測試 (重考)</strong></div><br />\n<br />\n香港市民：<br />\n✅ 以遊客身份入機場觀賞飛機升降 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n✅ 唔識路就坐多幾轉車 <img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/cook.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n✅ 必需繳付車資乘坐黨鐵<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/wet.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/lick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n其他國藉居民：<br />\n各有各做, 自由發揮 <img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/sowhat.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/nyixFQQ.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FnyixFQQ.png&h=cc1f24a6&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<div style=\"text-align: center;\"><strong>9月8日 (日) 2PM<br />\n香港人權與民主法案集會<br />\n美國駐港澳總領事館</strong></div><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/2GKH20p.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F2GKH20p.png&h=6178433f&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"655341390022fac35f210938ed4f22765d6523e7","tid":1534711,"uid":52571,"like":30,"dislike":1,"score":29,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-03T05:53:11.000Z","msg":"如果文尼有戴巴拿咁既樣<br />\n應該拎金球了"},{"pid":"0e884cb8dfea31bd6450c567b2968a9dac909de2","tid":1534711,"uid":19552,"like":60,"dislike":0,"score":60,"quote":{"pid":"655341390022fac35f210938ed4f22765d6523e7","tid":1534711,"uid":52571,"like":30,"dislike":1,"score":29,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-03T05:53:11.000Z","msg":"如果文尼有戴巴拿咁既樣<br />\n應該拎金球了"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-03T05:54:27.000Z","msg":"CHING有彭于晏樣都拎香港先生"},{"pid":"5f7689ac3f47d132bd10302bd9b17650afdf456a","tid":1534711,"uid":39912,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"0e884cb8dfea31bd6450c567b2968a9dac909de2","tid":1534711,"uid":19552,"like":60,"dislike":0,"score":60,"quote":{"pid":"655341390022fac35f210938ed4f22765d6523e7","tid":1534711,"uid":52571,"like":30,"dislike":1,"score":29,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-03T05:53:11.000Z","msg":"如果文尼有戴巴拿咁既樣<br />\n應該拎金球了"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-03T05:54:27.000Z","msg":"CHING有彭于晏樣都拎香港先生"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-03T05:56:03.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"58d1619f3ad0c469d67fc58c9b8e109397e8ada9","tid":1534711,"uid":38352,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"5f7689ac3f47d132bd10302bd9b17650afdf456a","tid":1534711,"uid":39912,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"0e884cb8dfea31bd6450c567b2968a9dac909de2","tid":1534711,"uid":19552,"like":60,"dislike":0,"score":60,"quote":{"pid":"655341390022fac35f210938ed4f22765d6523e7","tid":1534711,"uid":52571,"like":30,"dislike":1,"score